    "Name": "Havoc",
    "Details": "The Havoc mounted paired Diverse Optics ER medium lasers in each arm along with a Hovertec Quad SRM-4 launcher mounted in the center torso. The SRM-4 system was supplied with two tons of ammunition stored in a CASE II-protected storage area in the left torso, allowing the Havoc to carry specialty ammunition as needed.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Short</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.98</color></b>",
